import React from 'react'

const soundIcon = require("../../images/soudIcon.svg")

const VolumeSlider = () => {
  return (
    <SliderContainer>
      <SliderToggle src={soundIcon} />

      <SliderSection>
        <MusicIcon />
        <Slider type="range" min="1" max="100" value="50"/>
      </SliderSection>

      <SliderSection>
        <SoundIcon />
        <Slider type="range" min="1" max="100" value="50"/>
      </SliderSection>

    </SliderContainer>
  )
}

export default VolumeSlider
